      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>Clayton, son of Thomas Clayton, dec., and Ann {Clayton}
         Hunt, all of Richmond County {Va.}, apprentices himself to
         James Griffin, joiner, for the term of five years, beginning 9
         October 1745. Endorsed by M. Beckwith, Clerk of the Court for
         Richmond County.</p>
      </scopecontent>
